#. [message]: speaker=Mal-Skraat
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/03_An_Unexpected_Appearance.cfg:215
msgid "You have defeated my brother, but I will follow you and kill you!"
msgstr "你打败了我的兄弟，但我会追杀你到死！"

