msgstr "你个笨蛋！去找他。带他来见我！等等，不用了，见则杀之。"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:336
msgid "Look, the escaped prisoners have returned!"
