#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Weldyn_under_Attack.cfg:233
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "We will fight soon, my lord. Look, night approaches; they will soon "
